=== Noun ===
'''natural numbers'''

# {{set theory}} The [[set]] of [[positive]] [[integer]]s, {1, 2, 3, ...}, denoted as [[ℕ]].
# (''number theory, computer science'') The [[set]] of [[non-negative]] integers, ℕ = {0, 1, 2, 3, ...}, being the smallest such that:
#: 0[[∈]]ℕ, and
#: ''[[n]]''∈ℕ[[⇒]] ''[[succ]]''(''n'')∈ℕ.

